{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_teng_yi","text":"二哥有什么心事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":155,"line_start":30,"line_end":31},{"speaker":"char_teng_yi","speaker_name":"滕翼","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"我正在想，吕不韦为何一副有恃无恐的样子，他难道不怕你偕同鹿公等人一举把他擒杀吗？随他来田猎的虽都是一等一的高手，但人数只在百人之间，就算再多上几个管中邪也没有用。","tone":"沉声","chapter":155,"line_start":34,"line_end":37},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_teng_yi","text":"问题是他知道我使不动禁卫军，何况他还以为储君会护着他这仲父，那我们岂敢轻举妄动？","tone":"陈述","chapter":155,"line_start":40,"line_end":41},{"speaker":"char_teng_yi","speaker_name":"滕翼","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"这不像莫傲的作风，一直以来，他每一步都掌握主动，而我们只是苦苦的化解抵挡，在这么重要的时刻，他怎会现出漏洞？","tone":"陈述","chapter":155,"line_start":44,"line_end":45},{"speaker":"char_teng_yi","speaker_name":"滕翼","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"这么重要的场合，为何却见不到田单的爱将旦楚？","tone":"疑问","chapter":155,"line_start":50,"line_end":51},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_teng_yi","text":"空想无益，只要我们提高警戒，不用怕他们。","tone":"微笑","chapter":155,"line_start":54,"line_end":55},{"speaker":"char_wu_ting_fang","speaker_name":"乌廷芳","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"好啊！项郎快看！轮到小俊登场了。","tone":"欣喜","chapter":155,"line_start":58,"line_end":59},{"speaker":"char_zhao_zhi","speaker_name":"赵致","listener":null,"text":"小俊真了得哩！","tone":"欣喜","chapter":155,"line_start":74,"line_end":74},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_ji_yan_ran","text":"纪才女若肯到场中表演枪法，包保喝彩声不逊于小俊。","tone":"调侃","chapter":155,"line_start":86,"line_end":87},{"speaker":"char_ji_yan_ran","speaker_name":"纪嫣然","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"嫣然只须夫君你的赞赏就行，何须众人的彩声呢？","tone":"温柔","chapter":155,"line_start":92,"line_end":93}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xiang_shao_long","name":"项少龙","alias":[],"identity":"秦国统领","faction":"faction_qin_guo_wang_shi","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior