{"segment":2,"line_start":101,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_lu_gong","speaker_name":"鹿公","listener":null,"text":"凡能连胜三场者，储君赐十块黄金，酌情封升，我大秦的儿郎们，给点真功夫让我们看看！","tone":"豪迈","chapter":155,"line_start":108,"line_end":109},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_teng_yi","text":"二哥会否下场试试管中邪的底细？","tone":"疑问","chapter":155,"line_start":122,"line_end":123},{"speaker":"char_teng_yi","speaker_name":"滕翼","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"正有此意。","tone":"微笑","chapter":155,"line_start":126,"line_end":126},{"speaker":"char_teng_yi","speaker_name":"滕翼","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"今趟有好戏上演，吕不韦分明是要杀嫪毐的威风，不教他有扬威立万的机会。","tone":"欣喜","chapter":155,"line_start":134,"line_end":135},{"speaker":"char_ji_yan_ran","speaker_name":"纪嫣然","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"吕不韦深悉嫪毐长短，派得鲁残下场，必定有七、八分把握。","tone":"无奈","chapter":155,"line_start":146,"line_end":147},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_ji_yan_ran","text":"这人应是擅长强攻硬打的悍将，以攻为主，吕不韦是想他甫出手就杀得嫪毐招架无力，大大出丑，贬低他在朱姬和秦人心中的地位。","tone":"陈述","chapter":155,"line_start":150,"line_end":151},{"speaker":"char_qin_qing","speaker_name":"琴清","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"项大人料敌如神，才是高明。","tone":"欣喜","chapter":155,"line_start":156,"line_end":156},{"speaker":"char_teng_yi","speaker_name":"滕翼","listener":null,"text":"鲁残中计了。","tone":"无奈","chapter":155,"line_start":172,"line_end":172},{"speaker":"char_zhao_zhi","speaker_name":"赵致","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"为何吕不韦不派管中邪下场？","tone":"疑问","chapter":155,"line_start":176,"line_end":176},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_zhao_zhi","text":"若派管中邪下场，那就是不留余地了。","tone":"微笑","chapter":155,"line_start":178,"line_end":179},{"speaker":"char_teng_yi","speaker_name":"滕翼","listener":null,"text":"样子长得好原来有这么多好处。","tone":"无奈","chapter":155,"line_start":192,"line_end":192},{"speaker":"char_lao_ai","speaker_name":"嫪毐","listener":"char_lu_can","text":"鲁兄剑术高明，本人自问胜不过。","tone":